rawContent:
With possibilities 
I start my day
Letting the breeze find my way
Expectations are at a high
Today
I will try
Watching birds take flight 
Encouraging enough 
to begin my fight
Within myself 
bravely I will try
Stretching my arms
wanting to fly

#poem
